# ============================================================
# Non-T2 Mac packages (2012–2017 models)
# ============================================================
# Split into two eras:
#   2012-2015: USB keyboard/trackpad — works out of box
#   2016-2017: SPI keyboard/trackpad — needs applespi driver
#
# We include everything for both eras so one ISO covers all.
# ============================================================

# --- GPU Switching (dual-GPU MacBooks) ---
mesa-utils

# --- SPI keyboard/trackpad (2016-2017 MacBook Pro/12" MacBook) ---
# These models use Apple SPI instead of USB for internal
# keyboard and trackpad. The applespi driver handles this.
# NOTE: applespi may be in mainline kernel 5.17+, but we
# ensure the support modules are loaded via initramfs config.
# The inject script will set up initramfs modules for:
#   applespi, intel_lpss_pci, spi_pxa2xx_platform

# --- Touch Bar (2016-2017 MacBook Pro with Touch Bar) ---
# apple-ibridge / apple-ib-tb handles the Touch Bar
# NOTE: Installed from source/DKMS in inject script if needed
